title: Dolphin +3 multiplayer Games (SSBB,MP9,MKWII) [WII EMU]
description:
includes
--------------
Dolphin 5.0-6000 (4. December 2017)
Super Smash Bros Brawl
Mario Kart WII
Mario Party 9

instructions
--------------
Mount with Daemon tool or other
Install, dont forget where you installed it
Open Dolphin
Click Open and navigate to your install dir. Youll find a folder called "Game"
Choose a game and start


You propably need to Configure your Controller for playing.

System Requirements:
---------------------
Emulation depends mostly on CPU. You should aim for at least a i5 with 3GHZ for the included Games. 
Midrange GPU is enough, something like a gtx 750 should be fine
